OL,3,CBristol becomes England's least
OL,4,Caffordable city for rent
OL,6,FCompared to London, people in Bristol
OL,7,Fpay around 45% of their salary on
OL,8,Frent, while those in the capital pay
OL,9,Faround 42%, meaning Bristol is more
OL,10,Funaffordable to live in than London.
OL,12,FThe data suggests over four years, the
OL,13,Faverage renting household in Bristol
OL,14,Fwill pay their landlord more than
OL,15,F#90,000.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
