OL,3,CBristol becomes England's least
OL,4,Caffordable city for rent
OL,6,FAccording to the Fair Renting Campaign
OL,7,Fgroup, it means Bristol's 'cost of
OL,8,Frent day' this year, the day where an
OL,9,Faverage renter's salary pays off their
OL,10,Faverage annual rent, is today
OL,11,F(Saturday June 13).
